Package com.cissbank.basiccissbankapi.entity.client

Class Individual

java.lang.Object
com.cissbank.basiccissbankapi.entity.client.Individual
@Entity public class Individual extends Object
Represents an Individual, a physical person. Fields according to: (pt-BR) BANCO CENTRAL DO BRASIL, Resolução n°2.025, or (en) Central Bank of Brazil, Resolution nº2,025. Not to be confused with a legal person.
